<h4>Do you like talking about movies, books, or whether you think there is life on other planets? </h4>
 <h4>OR how that dude's hair on Ancient Aliens just keeps growing...UP?</h4><h4>Well then this is the place for you!</h4> <h4>Sign up and in and let's get the topics of the day going!</h4>




<form method="post">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="four columns">
      <label for="NameInput">Your name</label>
      <input class="u-full-width" name="user_name" type="text" placeholder="Your name here" id="user_name">
    </div>
    <div class="four columns">
      <label for="EmailInput">Your email</label>
      <input class="u-full-width" name="user_email" type="email" placeholder="email@mailbox.com" id="user_email">
    </div>
    <div class="four columns">
      <label for="PasswordInput">Your password</label>
      <input class="u-full-width" name="user_password" type="password" placeholder="password" id="user_password_digest">
    </div>
    
  </div>
  <input class="button-primary" type="submit" value="Sign up">
  <input class="button-primary" type="submit" value="Sign in">
</form> 


